  "302 newton-meters of torque": "",
  "600 newton-meters of torque": "",
  "100 newton-meters of torque": "",
  "Torque = force x distance = 300 N x 2 m = 600 N-m. The child produces 600 newton-meters of torque about the fulcrum.": "",
  "On the same seesaw, where must a 600 N adult sit to balance the 300 N child at 2 m?": "",
  "1 meter from the fulcrum on the opposite side": "",
  "2 meters from the fulcrum on the opposite side": "",
  "4 meters from the fulcrum on the opposite side": "",
  "3 meters from the fulcrum on the opposite side": "",
  "For balance: child's torque = adult's torque. 300 N x 2 m = 600 N x d. 600 = 600d. d = 1 m. The adult must sit 1 meter from the fulcrum to balance.": "",
